name: Ryu
description:
He already decided
make him a source of evil
misleading people more than animals
make the earth a place to play

Tell the humans
that he will enslave them
make heaven a mirage
make hell feel like a hoax

Tell the descendants of Adam
he will create a dark war
and make faith slowly dim
until the face of a good person is covered with bruises

Tell humans the end of time
he will come with the army
spread sin in the contested desert
closing the truth in the name of humanity

However, not everything he can misguide
those who always keep their mouth
those who do not pursue luxury
they are God's chosen people
